twf_cc:guide.introduction.title=Introduction Chop Chop
twf_cc:guide.introduction.body=Chop Chop Add-On is a Survival time saver that helps you rapidly clear trees, giant mushrooms, vines, and Nether forests. Equip an Axe, and get Chop Chopping!%1%1Chop Chop Add-On also helps with Creative tasks: when you change game mode to Creative, re-open this book for more instructions.%1%1You can change your personal Settings and learn more about this project below:

twf_cc:guide.introduction_creative.title=Introduction (Creative)
twf_cc:guide.introduction_creative.body=Chop Chop Add-On is a Creative tool that helps you quickly delete groups of connected blocks. While in Creative game mode, break a block while holding this Guide Book in your main hand and watch the deletion roll over the world!%1%1Chop Chop Add-On also helps with Survival tasks: when you change game mode to Survival, re-open this book for more helpful instructions.

